last_episode_to_air.name: Cafe Banner
last_episode_to_air.overview: Danny, Zoe and the Junkyard Helpers find an old banner from a local cafe. Danny takes it to his friend Katy the Product Designer, who turns it into something useful. Meanwhile, Zoe and the Junkyard Helpers make use of a stack of old flower pots, and there are three new ideas for fun games you can make at home using old paper cups.

name: Junk Rescue
overview: Combining traditional crafts and creative child-led makes, Junk Rescue makes sustainability fun, showing how the things we throw away can be turned into something useful.
